_sText:
This is a simple, wooden, sniper/guard tower. The texture is from HL2, and is not meant to be the final texture, so by all means, if you use it, change it. In addition, since I made this prefab for someone else and do not personally own CS:S, the ladder doesn't actually work. If you use it, simply tie the actual ladder to a func_ladder before you run it in-game.

Lastly, if you use it, please let me know at the very least. Credit is appreciated.

That is all.
